cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC 

This paper involves the integration of mobile edge computing (MEC) and wireless power transfer (WPT) for self-sustainable Internet of Things (IoT) devices. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization techniques for maximizing computation rates, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper involves multi-antenna access points and task partitioning, which could suggest it belonging to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
